body_html: I don't think this is specific to XLA AOT -- the build errors are from bazel-out/host/bin/external/org_tensorflow/tensorflow/python/pywrap_tensorflow_internal.cc which I think is generated by SWIG. I suspect this is due to some new %includes in tensorflow/python/tensorflow.i, but I'm not really sure. @michaelisard - perhaps this is better handled by someone more familiar with that side of things?
